# Cursor rules for NutriPair

## Project overview
Single-file Cloudflare Worker. All logic lives in `src/index.js`.
No build step — deploy with `wrangler deploy --no-bundle`.

## Code style
- Use `var` (not `let`/`const`) inside the embedded browser `<script>` block to avoid scoping issues.
- All browser DOM manipulation via string concatenation — no template literals inside buildHTML().
- Event listeners via addEventListener only — no inline onclick attributes.
- Worker-side code can use modern ES2022+ (Cloudflare Workers supports it natively).

## Key constraints
- Do NOT change GROCERY_DATA item IDs (g1–g44) — they are stored in production KV.
- Do NOT change DEFAULT_PLAN day keys (lun/mar/mer/jeu/ven/sam/dim).
- Keep I18N values JSON-safe (no unescaped special characters).
- Always test with `npm run dev` before `npm run deploy`.

## File structure
src/index.js is the ONLY source file. Everything else is config.
